headline: Is Now the Right Time to Reassess Arista After a 56% Stock Surge?
summary: If you’re wondering whether to make a move with Arista Networks stock, you’re not alone. Over the past few years, watching this company’s climb has felt a bit like witnessing a rocket launch; that is, if rockets continued to gain altitude well after clearing the atmosphere. The numbers tell the story: up 407% in three years, a staggering 1,078% lift over five years, and even just in the past year, the stock has climbed 56%.
